{
  "name": "RPlog_Battle_of_Trandosha",
  "title": "The Trap at Trandosha",
  "summary": "A New Republic task force jumps into the Trandoshan system to strike at the New Sith Order's homeworld fleet, initially catching the poorly-positioned Sith ships off guard. The ambush is reversed when Naval Commander Axel Vichten springs his real trap: an Interdictor seals the system and three new Sith Leviathan-class Destroyers under Grand Inquisitor Aknar Koth'lyri drop in behind the Republic line, supported by swarms of never-before-seen Barb-class fighters. As the Leviathans annihilate the cruiser Red Reef and pin the fleet, A-wing pilot Marl 'Gambit' Jace duels Vichten in a daring game of chicken while Commander Rasi Cen aboard the corvette Audacity evacuates his crew and rams the Star Destroyer War Hawk to blast an escape corridor open. The arrival of an Imperial scouting party under Krieg divides the Sith, and the battered Republic survivors flee to Kashyyyk, having lost heavily but accomplished their objective.",
